1. Translation: The Concept of the Entanglement Engine
This text proposes a new form of propulsion technology based on the principles of Quantum Information Holography.
The Foundation: Just as the wheel harnessed friction and leverage, this new "wheel" harnesses Quantum State Vectors—fundamental units of spinning light that exist at the Planck scale.
The Mechanism: The universe is described as a field of black holes where "singularities" (dense nodes of information) are entangled with "holographic screens" (event horizons). This engine mimics that geometry. It uses a lattice of qubits (quantum bits) entangled across shells to create standing waves of probability.
The Propulsion: By shifting the phase (the alignment of the wave peaks) between entangled qubits, the engine alters the angular frequency. Since energy is proportional to angular frequency (
