), changing the spin creates momentum. This generates thrust without propellant, fuel, or combustion.
The Vessel: The ship is envisioned not as a metal rocket, but as a transparent, luminous sphere—a macroscopic quantum processor. It creates constant acceleration (1g), allowing it to reach near-light speeds silently and efficiently.
